# ----------------------------------------------------------------
# 3. JOURNAL PAGE CLEAN URLS — /shortcode  →  journal.html
#    Netlify passes the ?id= query string through transparently.
#    The browser URL stays as /pjmh; journal.html script reads
#    window.PEERCITE_JOURNAL_ID (set by router.js) instead of
#    URLSearchParams, so no query string is needed client-side.
# ----------------------------------------------------------------
